 <p id="Par62" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">As mentioned above, we keep track of the absolute level of exposure, a variable that is used only to ensure that no health benefits accrue at exposures below a given threshold level (described further below). The absolute exposure levels in the pre-mitigation case (where 
